The Polling Task Status  





There are the tasks statuses will be shown in this status bar:       

In progress -   The background Polling communication task is in progress;  

Just submitted - The background Polling communication  task is just submitted  and preparing 
polling task to start;  

To be terminated -       The background Polling communication task is now in termination  process ; 

Terminated -    Background Polling task is terminated;  

IDLE -   Background Polling task is idle


