The “Current Task Status” Bar:  

There is a few task statuses will be shown in this status bar:       

In progress -    The Posting task is in progress;  
Just submitted -  The Posting task is just submitted;  
To be terminated -   The Posting task is now in termination;  
Terminated -    The Posting task is terminated;  
IDLE -    The Posting task is idle  

